Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没办法给自己做事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and incapable of doing anything for myself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就走运了  我这位邋遢朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in luck, my slovenly friend
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以一边邋里邋遢地瘫在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you sit there wallowing in your filth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.38,0:01:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一边让蟹堡王现做美食给你外卖过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can let the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make and deliver your meal for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是外卖十分钟内没到你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If your food isn't in your hands in ten minutes or less
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就免免免
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's f-f-f
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,台词是  免费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The line is, "Free"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就他说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what he said
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's me money?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,820)}蟹堡王\N呼叫{\fnArial}KK-01KP
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们并不知道  蟹堡王的广告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little did they know their Krusty commercial
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟会进入卑鄙无耻的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would reach the ignoble eyes of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶帮眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the League of E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱油滋滋的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love those greasy Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  但我讨厌拿钱去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I hate paying for things
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是午后小零食到不了我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if I don't get my afternoon snackies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就狠狠发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna throw a tantrum
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以就要搞个超级邪恶的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This calls for a deliciously diabolical scheme
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给蟹堡王下单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We place our order with the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再使出我们的邪恶力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then use our powers of evil
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害外卖小哥超时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ensure the delivery boy is late
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就有免费午餐吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we get a free lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我笑吧  坏蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh with me, villains
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要五份蟹堡套餐  多加蟹堡酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like five Krabby Combos, extra Krusty sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改成四份  加一份儿童堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make that four and a Pipsqueak Patty kid's meal
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it out to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.98,0:02:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地址就在邪恶帮秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deliver to League of E.V.I.L. secret hideout
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油站后面的不祥巷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ominous Alley, behind the gas station
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.11,0:02:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Villains
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Battle stations
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,398)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now remember, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次的外卖一定得快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this delivery's gotta be quick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且得直接放到客人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you gotta put it directly in the customer's hand
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不想白送霸王餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't givin' out no free meals
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.12,0:03:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我能不能顺便找坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll have time for the villains
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我漫画签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to sign my comic book?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1528,158)}正联
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧进炮里就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get in the cannon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pull
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,砸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1394,292)}邪恶帮基地\N在这
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Secret entrance"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:36.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,262)}秘密入口
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就有反派本色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds villainous
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the place
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝急中生智
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thinking quickly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿出了水动力锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob reached for his hydrodynamic spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还带着左右铲配件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with port and starboard attachments
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还剩八分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eight minutes to spare
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半会跟公园散步一样轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll be a walk in the park
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  洞穴散步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, cave
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想干嘛  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whattaya want, bub?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重罪犯海伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Helen the Felon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱惹麻烦的熊孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The trouble-making tyke
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要关你禁闭  害你超时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm giving you a time-out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可  可我要送外卖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-But I'm making a delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说我得送到你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Krabs says I have to put it right in your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是射线恶魔手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray's hand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想找到他  就得先打开这扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to open this door
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you wanna get to him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.96,0:04:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放弃外卖袋吧  小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give up the bag, buddy boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对不可能准时到射线恶魔那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never make it to Man Ray on time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没力气  转不动把手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too weak to turn knob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就使出我的翻肉饼手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll use my patty flipping hand
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No fair
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那是作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's cheatin'
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,脑震荡
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说我能找你要签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还剩六分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six minutes to spare
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨霸虾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumbo Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行为最恶劣的头号人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The biggest name in bad behavior
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.04,0:05:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪儿  小薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just where do you think you're going, small fry?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹  蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-Krusty delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Man Ray?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想找他  就得先过我这关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you wanna get to him, you'll have to go through me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,小不点
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你漫画形象看着大多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look bigger in the comics
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以给我签下名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could sign this for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.98,0:06:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gladly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是粉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're a fan?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是铁粉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你还没完呢  小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not done with you, little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就剩四分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1182,298)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1234,490)}闪亮又干净
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是拐错弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,must have taken a wrong turn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1598,360)}未来的清洁剂\N查理泡泡\N顽固污渍我来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1804,358)}×
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  你这笨海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You certainly did, you simpleminded sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好深深陷入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be ensnared by the--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能找你签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,爆
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where's Man Ray?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-Krusty d-delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该料到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have known
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底番茄潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sub-Marinara
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶的肉丸潜艇堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The maniacal meatball sub
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不会被食物给打败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could never be defeated by food
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,俏皮
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两面包夹
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被食物打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been defeated by food
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只邪恶的三明治正准备着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sinister spuccadella is preparing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把我们的英雄泡进他举世闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to marinate our hero in his famous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.77,0:08:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灼热意式香辣番茄酱里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,extra spicy molten arrabbiata sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝会如何摆脱这三明治的魔爪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How will SpongeBob escape this harrowing hoagie?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  旁白先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Narrator
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then do it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我面包吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I filled up on bread
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1091,920)}填 满
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该打包剩菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to wrap up the leftovers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sign this for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你又被挫败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been foiled again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1092,920)}锡箔纸
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,超新鲜
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然还在等外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While I wait for my delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就趁机打发点时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might as well kill some time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨鼻侠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tremendous Trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子能通晓一切的象海豹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The elephant seal whose nose knows all
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我走  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经闻出你的邪恶事迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've already sniffed out your evil deeds
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你唯一会闻到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing you'll be sniffing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这块臭奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is this stinky cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别放林堡奶酪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not Limburger
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have children
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还剩十秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And with ten seconds to spare
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的午餐外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My lunch order
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.31,0:09:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来放我手上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, go ahead and put it in my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外卖已送达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Delivery complete
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it was
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超时一秒钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one second late
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,超时
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That means
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our meal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is free
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘲笑他吧  坏蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh at him, villains
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little help here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  巨鼻侠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Tremendous Trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll free you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能找你要签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就签
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But listen, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你帮了我  那我也会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you helped me, so I'll help you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨鼻侠使出他巨鼻的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the prodigious power of his potent proboscis
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.83,0:10:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个喷嚏就带海绵宝宝穿越回了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tremendous Trunk sneezed SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back through time itself
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一分钟零七秒前
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已送达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,delivered
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共12块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be $12
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you see
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶帮其实破产了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The League of E.V.I.L. is actually broke
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果犯罪就是得不偿失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turns out crime doesn't pay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll cover it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们送的小费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the tip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sign here, please
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们  坏蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, evil villains
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.79,标准-Chi,,500,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.79,标准-Eng,,500,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.92,标准-Chi,,500,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.92,标准-Eng,,500,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.84,标准-Chi,,500,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.84,标准-Eng,,500,0,0,,Gesundheit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.84,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 专用于礼貌回复打喷嚏者的套话 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,本集完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.55,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp45}我的老爸\N{\fs30} \N{\fs175}是条船
