Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(650,494)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(814,710)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,538)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我钱远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于想好可以让你买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally figured out what you can get me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我下周的生日礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for my birthday next week
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到了最适合你买给我的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found the perfect boat for you to buy me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没说要给你买船当生日礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never said I'd buy you a birthday boat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你把那震耳欲聋的音乐关了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you stop playing that earsplitting music
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就给你买条新船当你生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a new boat for your birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没在偷偷录音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not recording me, are ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.27,0:12:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这条船适合我  价格只要一万块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the only boat for me and it's only 10,000 clams
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,T-t-t-t-ten
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Th-th-th-thousand?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新船要到手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gonna get a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不害人愁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not bratty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日礼物船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A birthday boat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要老爸送给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From my daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真多嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and my big mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我女儿的生日礼物船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me daughter's birthday boat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是小册子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the brochure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破烂老爷船不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice fixer-upper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是干嘛不直接买条新船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but why didn't you just buy a new boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.64,0:13:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我才不花一万冤枉钱买新船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not paying 10,000 clams for a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得来给我修理这条船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna help me fix up this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要修得跟小册子上的船一样好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so it's as good as the brochure boat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家珍珍肯定看不出区别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me Pearl will never know the difference
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能得要一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This may take a while
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,过了一个一阵子后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zow-ie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这船一看就像是值一百万的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This boat looks like it costs a million clams
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少外观确实像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least on the outside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁珍珍没醒  找来发动机就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we just gotta find an engine before Pearl wakes up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到我生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta hide
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍要来了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl's a-coming, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新船要到手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gonna get a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不害人愁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not bratty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日礼物船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A birthday boat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要老爸送给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From my daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来一条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-O-A-T
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,768)}珍珍
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是我要的船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the boat that I wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love my daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来试驾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a test drive
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没等老爸醒来  我就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be back before Daddy wakes up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她没发动机开不了船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She can't drive a boat with no engine
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让她发现这船是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She can't find out this is a piece of junk
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how will we do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假装呗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fake it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩当发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be the engine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来火力全开  看看这船有什么本事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's open her up and see what this baby can do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子宝宝  我的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy-Bob, me sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你负责转船轴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on axle duty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-Aye, Cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有导航系统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A navigation system
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去裤头村高中最快的路是哪条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the quickest route to Bikini Bottom High School?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去接我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to pick up my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油腻青少年休想上这条船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want any greasy teenagers in this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.83,0:15:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前方路口左转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn left at the intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,330)}高中
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你船好酷啊  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool boat, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闲聊了  姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit gawking, girls
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and hop in
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来放点音乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have some music
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开嗓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start singing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ears
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧关了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut it off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望她们没把我壳给摔裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope they didn't crack my shell open
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刹车  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你船不错嘛  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice wheels, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到你爸这样的铁老公鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought an old skinflint like your dad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会给你买条船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would buy you a boat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这小流氓说谁老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's this hoodlum calling old?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚远点  鲨老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a hike, Sharkface
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非鲨鱼想比一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless you want a shark race?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦队想比一把是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cheerleader race, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿好你们的啦啦球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on to your pom-poms
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比比  比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,R-r-r-race?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A race?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一边凉快去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a break, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来搞定这个飞机头混账
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This pompadoured punk is mine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,606)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  不觉得我们该开慢一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, don't you think we should slow down a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不能慢下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't slow down now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这兔崽子已经被我捏得死死的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got this snot-nose right where I want him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(758,920)}用 牙
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全力应对那些玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sink your teeth into those
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.93,注释,,0,0,0,,[ defeat（挫败）与 feet（脚）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挫败感真难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The agony of defeat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你腿全给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need all your legs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再生越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As fast as you can grow 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell a plan
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  小船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, boat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sic 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦队就该老实待在运动场的草皮上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheerleaders should stay on their astro-turf
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来上路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and off the road
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些玩意好像不小心掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You seem to have dropped these
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的心跳得比那几条鲨鱼还快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My heart is racing faster than those sharks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要更多刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want more excitement
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更多惊险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More thrills
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要狠狠狂开这条船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More vehicular mayhem
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就比如说撞船大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like a demolition derby
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就比如说撞船大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like a demolition derby
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My boat is invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,184)}撞船大赛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们的鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's our whale
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体积庞大绝不出局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She is much too big to fail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我的珍珍女生转身回身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my Pearl Girl Twirl Hurl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再不逃出去  就会被珍珍害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we don't get out of here, Pearl's gonna get us killed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要尝尝我的呼吸孔狂射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a Blowhole Blast
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个大猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a rush
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下正是撞船鲸神  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a demolition whale, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我新船怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I do to my new boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸会宰了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's gonna kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这声音听着不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点像我爸上厕所的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like my dad in the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我听来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds to me like
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你发动机在缓慢痛苦地濒临一死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your engine is dying a slow, agonizing death
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱去把这船顶起来  修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get it on the lift and fix 'er up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,456)}修船厂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,196)}汽船零件
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐  我找到问题所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, young lady, I found the trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你船上就俩白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got two knuckleheads
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,instead of an engine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你躲在我船里面干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing hiding inside of my boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是给你想造一条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to build you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别的礼物船  庆祝你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a special boat for your birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟她解释  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell her, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ooh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不花一万冤枉钱买新船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not payin' 10,000 clams for a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍肯定看不出区别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl will never know the difference
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没你事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我说  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱这应该只是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think what we have here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,互相体谅没到位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is simply a failure to commiserate
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听够你的话了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough from you, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是老样子  想贪便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You tried to cheap out like always
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还送我垃圾当生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and gift me a piece of junk for my birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那种说法就有点难听了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, when you say it like that it sounds bad, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明白真正的问题所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see the real trouble now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你口袋里不是有张信用卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a credit card in your pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以拿它来付款
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that needs charging
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要用这卡来买一条新船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna charge a new boat on it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两条也行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe two
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.34,0:22:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边正好有两条新船待售
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just happen to have two new boats for sale right here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这俩船可贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they're very expensive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.10,0:22:18.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:18.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两条船到手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got two boats
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不害人愁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not bratty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两条船到手  狠狠损我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got two boats to spite my daddy
